      <link>https://blog.cowbay.org/p/%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98-%E7%94%A8zfs%E7%9A%84snapshot-%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%BE%86%E5%81%9A-postgresql-%E7%9A%84%E5%82%99%E4%BB%BD%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F-/-postgresql-backup-restore-using-zfs-snapshot/</link>
